        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Please support this petition which is asking <a href="/medway_council" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="17973642"><s>@</s><b>medway_council</b></a> to open a public consultation about the horrendous changes to parking permits. Please sign and RT <a href="https://t.co/0dlaqrg2dH" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://you.38degrees.org.uk/petitions/visitor-parking-permits?bucket=&amp;source=twitter-share-button" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="https://you.38degrees.org.uk/petitions/visitor-parking-permits?bucket=&amp;source=twitter-share-button"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">you.38degrees.org.uk/petitions/visi</span><span class="invisible">tor-parking-permits?bucket=&amp;source=twitter-share-button</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a><a href="https://t.co/Rt4PMP7hwn" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/Rt4PMP7hwn</a></p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Absolutely. Policy not personality. She fails on both <a href="/hashtag/LabourManifesto?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>LabourManifesto</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/forthemanynotthefew?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>forthemanynotthefew</b></a><a href="https://t.co/xlYVoAvlSH" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/IanDunt/status/871678286237229057" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/IanDunt/status/871678286237229057"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/IanDunt/status</span><span class="invisible">/871678286237229057</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Cllr Teresa Murray added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">We are all shocked and angry today - but this is our city. We will never let these cowards win and we will never be cowed by terrorism.<a href="https://t.co/o7ZMwg28mv" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/o7ZMwg28mv</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Events for Friday 26th May
11am -12pm - WASPI Stall on Rochester High Street - come find us there.

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Months of campaigning by Labour members for local &amp; mayoral elections topped off by a brilliant GOTV effort.
